full_text: Dogecoin has rocketed more than 7,252% so far this year, taking its market value to well over $40 billion, minting a number of millionaires on paper. https://t.co/NofQaIYDIf

localize.full_text: Dogecoinは今年に入ってから7,252%以上の急上昇を見せ、その市場価値は400億ドルをはるかに超え、多くの億万長者を生み出しています。https://t.co/NofQaIYDIf。
